1. *Otvorila* sam prozor da bih pustila vazduh. (I opened* the window to let some air in.)
2. Kada sam stigla, vrata su već bila *otvorena*. (When I arrived, the doors were already *open*.)
3. Ona će uskoro *otvoriti* novi restoran u centru grada. (She will soon *open* a new restaurant in the city center.)
4. Nakon što je primio paket, momak ga je brzo *otvorio*. (After receiving the package, the guy quickly *opened* it.)
5. *Otvorili* smo novu knjižaru u našem kraju. (We *opened* a new bookstore in our neighborhood.)
6. Kada su čuli zvuk, brzo su *otvorili* vrata i pogledali šta se događa. (When they heard the sound, they quickly *opened* the door and looked to see what was happening.)
7. *Otvori* prozor, molim te. (Please, *open* the window.)
8. Ona je uvek spremna da *otvori* srce i sasluša svoje prijatelje. (She is always ready to *open* her heart and listen to her friends.)
9. Kada sam *otvorila* frižider, primetila sam da je sve pokvareno. (When I *opened* the fridge, I noticed that everything was spoiled.)
10. Nikada neću zaboraviti kada sam prvi put *otvorila* oči i ugledala svoju porodicu. (I will never forget when I first *opened* my eyes and saw my family.)